snippet.title: THE UTILITY ROOM - VR Gameplay Teaser #1
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2091960/The_Utility_Room/
Subreddit: 
https://www.reddit.com/r/TheUtilityRoom/

The Utility Room VR game takes you to the 'behind the scenes' of the Universe. Beyond a door lies a barren landscape inhabited by strange stonefaced beings. Here, the maintenance and heavy lifting required keeps existence stable and temporal. You are a tourist. Don't do anything foolish.
